| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-0203 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: c25a0bcf-9317-5c8e-a7df-bc20f28f38dd"
